DAY 1 - INTRODUCTION TO BACKEND

TASK: 
*install flask/django
*create basic backend project
*run server on browser
*display welcome message

how to install flask?
step1: install flask-open terminal /command prompt and enter "pip install flask" command 

step 2: create first flask application -file named app,py which contain code
 *Flask(__name__)-creates flask app
 *@app.route('/')- connects the home URL to a func
 *func returns text 
 *app.run()-starts the local server 

step 3: run flask application using command python app.py and it will show the local server address, open this URL in browser to view.

